WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.885
Because AppsFlyer is a software solution, successfully selling our platform

00:00:03.885 --> 00:00:07.770
does not immediately expand a customer's underlying cloud compute spend

00:00:07.770 --> 00:00:11.655
on day one. Professional Insight: Assuming an Amazon Account Manager

00:00:11.655 --> 00:00:15.540
will automatically support your deal out of goodwill is a

00:00:15.540 --> 00:00:19.425
critical logical flaw. Their behavior is strictly governed by their

00:00:19.425 --> 00:00:23.310
quota targets. If your solution does not demonstrably drive their

00:00:23.310 --> 00:00:27.195
specific growth goals, you will not receive their advocacy. You

00:00:27.195 --> 00:00:31.080
must actively and aggressively sell our distinct value proposition directly

00:00:31.080 --> 00:00:34.965
to them, explicitly proving that prioritizing our solution actively drives

00:00:34.965 --> 00:00:38.850
their specific, individual growth goals.
